def karatsuba(num1, num2):
    if num1 < 10 or num2 < 10:
        return num1 * num2
    n1 = len(str(num1))
    n2 = len(str(num2))
    N = max(n1, n2)
    N += N & 1
    (a, b) = divmod(num1, 10 ** (N // 2))
    (c, d) = divmod(num2, 10 ** (N // 2))
    ac = karatsuba(a, c)
    bd = karatsuba(b, d)
    ad_plus_bc = karatsuba(a + b, c + d) - ac - bd
    return 10 ** N * ac + bd + 10 ** (N // 2) * ad_plus_bc
